sentences: Catman (born David Taieb in 1971), son of Willy Lewis, famous french drummer, is a French musician and electronic music producer from Paris.
His first solo album, released in 2003, featured Piers Faccini, Sub-Z, Susie One, Vincent Ségalw and Seb Martel.
